column5: Right on man, nice bunch of fish! What did you catch 'em on?
a hook...lol   nice fish love back lakes
Gorgeous fish, my kind of trip!  We've only had ice out here for about 5 days so the Lakers have been busy but specks are a ways off.  Is this ON or QC?
Some real beauties there , love the back lakes . Thanks for sharing !!!
It looks like you've got a couple hidden gems there. Beauty fish!
Incredible fish & spot, thanks for posting!!
Wow. Some super nice fish there. Great report.
Beautiful fish, always nice when your hard work is rewarded
Wicked!  Love me some of that action right about meow..
Beauty!!!!   Well done boys, what a great trip
That was a very nice pic report.  A great week well spent.  Congrats  Ven

Thanks for the kind comments gang! Right on man, nice bunch of fish! What did you catch 'em on? The lakers were caught on gold 1/4oz Little Cleos and the specks were caught with various spinners and spoons.
I too love fishing in track pants.  A guilty pleasure of mine.
